{"tid":1831800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大同學記得戴口罩同清潔hall!!!","createTime":"2020-01-20T16:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T01:26:43.000Z","uid":203799,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9773c29feb32885ac6fdb642aab47e0f58bcb2d3","tid":1831800,"uid":203799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:13:57.000Z","msg":"From telegram<br />\n<br />\n北座有中國學生感染肺炎 現仍住宿<br />\n<br />\n【浸大編委訊】據學生會幹事會內務副幹事長林穎澤指，<span style=\"color: red;\">本科生舍堂北座15樓有一名中國學生報稱於日前在深圳求醫後確診肺炎，雖未確認是否為武漢肺炎，但仍居留於宿舍。</span><br />\n<br />\n學生會隨後通報學生事務處及舍堂組，周樹人堂舍堂主任陳嘉榮稱現正跟進情況，並拒絕透露詳情。<br />\n<br />\n該名染病學生現跟隨舍堂主任、舍監及Non-local mentor外出求醫。<br />\n<br />\n本會呼籲同學注意個人衛生，出門時佩戴口罩，減低被傳染及患病的機會。本會將繼續關注事件。"},{"pid":"e7695c15de0e0d0c3da2f3140590eb9f570296b1","tid":1831800,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:14:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de326dc97a347f8d56e51d1f0be608112b892f52","tid":1831800,"uid":308496,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"係！知道！一定聽哂絲打講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe7996c6fea2d85350c09711471ad7b09c8baf6","tid":1831800,"uid":203799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de326dc97a347f8d56e51d1f0be608112b892f52","tid":1831800,"uid":308496,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"係！知道！一定聽哂絲打講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6f84a33278a9d0f